Pre-Cryptaine Era vs. The Future

Let’s compare the rusty processes and features of the traditional system with the future of commission payments revolutionized by Cryptaine.

“Traditional” Affiliate Model

Cryptaine

Payment cycles

Slow payment cycles that require long execution times (30-60 days).

Payment cycles can be completed almost instantly.

Payment methodes

Limited payment methods by region. No support for certain payment gateways.

Blockchain-based payments ensure that both affiliates and vendors have no limitations of any sort.

Attribution

Attribution & revenue may be lacking due to traditionally flawed attribution systems.

Blockchain smart contracts information backup allows seamless and reliable attribution for all sources of traffic.

Transperancy

Systems are typically opaque and do not allow for third-party audits.

Blockchain technology enables full transparency and allows anyone to check any of the campaign statistics inside blockchain.

Fairness

Vendors are able to “cut” revenue streams and reduce commissions.

An immutable, fair system that is applicable to all partners, contracts, and conditions.

Community

Usually doesn’t have an open community and makes it hard to get into the “inner circle” of affiliates and vendors.

We maintain a strong community of enthusiasts who can either quickly drive the traffic or give advice on improvements of the campaign.

Ease of integration

Requires partial or full renovation of the selling model in order to include the affiliate program where it didn’t exist.

Ability to quickly integrate our affiliate system into any already existing project, on-chain or off-chain, working on any technological base.

Our smart contracts secure key transactions between vendors and affiliates, automatically executing payouts and tracking significant sales data,while eliminating payment delays and disputes common in traditional systems.
